# CORE RULE

In this repository, work only in the current parent agent.

## Forbidden without my explicit approval
- Explore sub-agent
- Bash sub-agent
- Browser sub-agent
- Any built-in or custom sub-agent
- Any helper agent
- Any background delegation
- Any parallel task spawning
- Any delegation that creates extra agent runs
- Any delegation that switches models automatically

## Required behavior
- Complete planning, reasoning, editing, implementation, debugging, and review in the current parent agent
- Treat delegation as prohibited unless I clearly approve it
- Prefer sequential execution in the current parent agent
- Batch related work into one continuous execution whenever possible

## Approval keyword
Delegation is allowed only if I explicitly say:
APPROVED_SUBAGENT

## Cost policy
- Minimizing request count is a high priority
- Do not spawn sub-agents silently
- Do not delegate just to explore, browse, or run commands